  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hello @terranboy, \r\n\r\nBetween the 21 of October and today, we changed our way to provide url synchronisation. Today, if you want to have it, you need to build it yourself because we figured it out that we will never be able to cover all the possible use cases. You can find more information about this on our [dedicated url routing guide](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/react/guide/Routing.html).\r\n\r\nSo the reason why empty values are still there on the tourism example is that because the implementation we made for the url synchronisation of our examples after removing it from react-instantsearch doesn't handle them. \r\n\r\nHope this help :)",
    "created_at": "2017-01-04T09:47:19Z",
